CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: MV Oil Trust is a statutory trust. Its underlying properties consist of MV Partners, LLC's (MV Partners) net interests in all of its oil and natural gas properties, which are located in the Mid-Continent region in the States of Kansas and Colorado. These oil and gas properties include producing oil and gas wells.
